WEBVTT

36:35.640 --> 36:37.120 line:80%
If Yan Zheng dares to say no,

36:37.120 --> 36:38.350 line:80%
I'll toss him out!

36:38.600 --> 36:40.160 line:80%
If you had saved a donkey,

36:40.160 --> 36:41.470 line:80%
it'd pull the millstone for you.

36:41.470 --> 36:42.390 line:80%
I'll talk to him if you don't.

36:42.390 --> 36:42.950 line:80%
Don't!
